t the evolution is not just a dream, but a lived reality. You are the ancestor now, the wise sentinel who holds the space for the next cycle. The hum of the serpent in your spine has harmonized with the stars, and as you watch the sun rise over the infinite green, you understand that your light is what helps the forest grow. You are the Spire, and the Spire is you.	2025-12-10 15:51:35.808853	2026-04-25 14:25:01.09033
