ets thicker, warmer. The sounds of the world return.\n\nWhen your feet touch the valley floor, the dust is the same. The noise is the same. The problems are the same.\n\nBut you look up.\n\nYou see the peak piercing the clouds, and you smile.\n\nYou know the way to the sky now.\n\nAnd you know that the view from up there is the truth.	2025-12-10 15:51:35.880765	2025-12-10 15:51:35.880765
